ca.cumulonimbus.pressurenetsdk
Class CbDb

java.lang.Object
  ca.cumulonimbus.pressurenetsdk.CbDb

public class CbDb
extends java.lang.Object

Keep track of app settings, as this SDK may be used by more than one app on a device. This allows an empty Intent to start the Service generically, and we can then read saved settings for each registered app to act accordingly.

Author:
jacob
